title: UNLV looking for rebound season with talented roster
text: UNLV looking for rebound season with talented roster Thursday, 22 October 2015 (23 seconds ago) LAS VEGAS (AP) Dave Rice knew there would be pressure when he took the job at UNLV. He played on the Runnin' Rebels' 1990 championship team and spent 11 seasons as an assistant at the school, so he understood the expectations in Sin City.
